Dear All,

All these are for the novice.

When you transcend, there is no difference between Him and you !

Dont be like the Bible people who quote from verses, highlighting the page, without understanding what is implied.

I am not decrying Nama Japa.

Namamanu Adbhutha Swargam
Namamanu Punarbaham
Namamanu Maha Siddhi
Namamanu Samasthavum

